{
  "stem": "17426.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 144.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was supposed to know when the man of the house uttered the first word what he wanted and what he meant to say.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I was supposed to reply-- for example, as he would say, 'and,' then I would say, I will pick you up tonight, and I will have this and this ready, I will have this and this.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the play went down as the parents left and the daughter was alone, they-- she invited some friends, all university students, as she was, for a party.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they drank some spirits.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in comes a local, very poor Jew, who was regarded as a [NON-ENGLISH], as a dummy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was made fun of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then finally, they asked him-- after making lots of fun of him, and he kind of meek, walking around-- ask him, if you were to marry anyone of these girls, who would you like to marry?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he wouldn't respond.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, leave me alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to marry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of these young university students lifted up his finger and pointed at the daughter of the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] faith behold, they put them on next to each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in fun, they married him, and he had to say [NON-ENGLISH], all those words that are in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the father came back, he came just in as they were married.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, what have you done?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are married to this man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what in our faith, you must be his wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or else you must divorce.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- we have to stop this tape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll continue with this story on tape number two shortly.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
